Wescoal Says Court Application to Shut Unit Down Set Aside, Pursues Claim

-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 
2011-08-03T06:06:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-03/wescoal-says-court-application-to-shut-unit-down-set-aside-pursues-claim.html
Wescoal Holdings Ltd. (WSL)  said the North
Gauteng High Court set aside an application by Sutha Civials
Ltd. for the winding up of its Wescoal Mining (Pty) Ltd. unit.  Wescoal will be pursuing a “substantial” damages claim
against Sutha, it said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vernon Wessels at 
 vwessels@bloomberg.net  